import { Flex, Spacer, Box, Center } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import Logo from "../atoms/Logo"
import MenuBar from "../atoms/MenuBar"

const Header = () => {
    return (
        <>
        <Box h='70px' bg='red'>
            <Flex align='center' justify='space-between' h='70px'>
                <Box ml='20px'>
                    <Logo />    
                </Box>
                <Box>
                    <MenuBar />
                </Box>
            </Flex>

        </Box>
        </>
    )
}

export default Header
